  <hr/>
  <a name="wfaudio26_2.2"/>
  <p><strong>Frederick Gwynn:</strong>Is Candace a common name in Mississippi or&#x2014;?</p>
  <hr/>
  <p><strong>William Faulkner:</strong>No. No, Caddy seemed a nice name for her, and I had to think of
