                    could even apply enough physical force when necessary to keep him in hand. It's
                    like the lion tamer is&#x2014;is a man. It means simply that he's big enough
                    for his job. That's what Luster&#x2014;I meant by that. In Luster's
                    terminology, a man is anyone who is big enough to do what he has to
                        do.
                </p>
