                </p>
  <hr/>
  <a name="wfaudio26_2.15"/>
  <p><strong>William Faulkner:</strong>Sorry.</p>
  <hr/>
  <p><strong>Unidentified participant:</strong>I was wondering in your Indian stories again, "Lo!" and "A Courtship" and
                    in "A Justice," except for the framework, your stories&#x2014;these stories
